{"tid":2408362,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獨居老人辭世　遺囑指定5百萬美金財產給8歲愛犬繼承","createTime":"2021-02-15T00:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T11:26:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":144,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"0653d73c894a3ccc4749f1c20bee78cfe63a3579","tid":2408362,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"美國田納西州一名獨居老人日前因病辭世，死前立下遺囑，將他美金5百萬元(約台幣1.4億元)遺產，交由他8歲的愛犬繼承，狗狗一夕之間成了億萬富翁。<br />\n<br />\n《福斯新聞》報導，田納西州納許維爾市老翁多利斯(Bill Dorris)，是一名成功的企業家，始終沒有結婚，去年年底因病辭世。他在生前留下遺囑，要將美金5百萬元的財產，全部交付信託，用來照顧他心愛的LuLu後半輩子。<br />\n<br />\nLuLu是多利斯飼養的一頭邊境牧羊犬(border collie)，今年8歲，目前由多利斯的好友柏頓(Martha Burton)代為照顧，柏頓表示：「他真的很愛狗，平常出外旅行時都交給我照顧」。<br />\n<br />\n今年已高齡88歲的柏頓說，LuLu將會有吃不完的狗糧，還可以請私人保鑣，「牠真的是個好女孩」，柏頓很清楚知道，自己不太可能在LuLu身上花掉這5百萬美元，她仍笑著說：「好吧，我盡量試試看」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/WVJ3LYXJB5D5TNBPL3LSTWF4PM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FWVJ3LYXJB5D5TNBPL3LSTWF4PM%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4efrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=a09eda6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FWVJ3LYXJB5D5TNBPL3LSTWF4PM%2F&h=f1c51376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/WVJ3LYXJB5D5TNBPL3LSTWF4PM/</a>"},{"pid":"311f9fc3f8f3e323ae0117af80d50a6e31e92bd4","tid":2408362,"uid":58609,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:42:52.000Z","msg":"汪汪汪"},{"pid":"22cb9c4108b21099c9bf3acb57d5e738388e4036","tid":2408362,"uid":130044,"like":365,"dislike":2,"score":363,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"一夜之間變成 貴婦狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae87158c80780724aa501c1335cff23c5f3fb23","tid":2408362,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":130,"score":-125,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"咁撚有錢都唔撚結婚,係咪真係好撚驚八達通分你身家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/d